INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3172, 'enUS', 'Salutations.  My function is to offer access to and, when permissible, insight into information regarding the Creators\' synthesis of the Earthen on the world designated as Azeroth.  I am ready to share this information with you now at your leisure.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3173, 'enUS', 'The Earthen are a synthesized race engineered by the Creators, functioning as one of the seed races in the initial population of the world designated as Azeroth.  The Earthen were created to aid the Creators\' efforts in shaping the deep regions of this world.$B$BThey are a modification of the standard subterranean being matrix used on other worlds that the Creators have seeded.  The construction of this prototype race created various anomalies that were observed after initial synthesis.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3174, 'enUS', 'It is one of the synthesis matrices the Creators use when seeding a world.  Each synthesis matrix is used to achieve the Creators\' goals.  For Azeroth, a subterranean being matrix was modified to create a being with increased durability with an affinity for deep region shaping; the Earthen are the product of this modification.$B$BAfter the Earthen had been put into service for the Creators, unforeseen anomalies were discovered that affected their synthesis matrix due to high-stress environments.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3175, 'enUS', 'Additional background information on the Earthen must be given to you before this question may be answered properly.$B$BProcessing.$B$BTo understand the anomalies of the Earthen, it is first important to understand what the Earthen represent in their design intent.  The Earthen represent the Creators\' attempt at improving the survivability paradigm of the standard subterranean being matrix.  This was done by incorporating a resilient foundation of construction inherent to the world into said matrix.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3176, 'enUS', 'It is the baseline material used in race synthesis.  A cross-section of Azeroth\'s crust was used as the foundation for the Earthen\'s synthesis rather than the typical biomass construction foundation used by the Creators.$B$BResearch on the world\'s composition led the Creators to theorize that an enhanced being could be synthesized that would epitomize the resiliency of this world\'s essence.  This was accomplished by choosing to use a blend of Azeroth\'s various stone core compounds as the foundation.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3177, 'enUS', 'Simply stated, this is correct.$B$BThe Earthen\'s physical features are that of a smaller stature humanoid, though their composition is that of Azeroth\'s various stone core compounds.  Their design maximizes strength and stamina without sacrificing cognitive processing power.  Their skin and musculature are nearly impervious to physical damage, and with very minor modifications the Earthen display a remarkable resiliency to unwanted magical forces.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3178, 'enUS', 'It is integral to the assimilation of this data that it is understood that the Creators wanted to synthesize a race that would long be an integral part of this world\'s development cycle after they had departed.  This race would be instrumental in fulfilling the Creators\' long-term development objectives for Azeroth.  $B$BAs an ancillary note, the nomenclature \"Earthen\" was deemed apropos for the new race by the Creators, based on the Earthen\'s composition.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3179, 'enUS', 'The Earthen\'s only anomaly in synthesis is the tendency for matrix destabilization while being utilized in high-stress environments.$B$BAddendum: deep earth sculpting was naturally suited to the new matrix design and thus never met the qualifications of duplicating a high-stress environment.$B$BDestabilization was not discovered until well into the Earthen\'s primary service cycle for the Creators.  The Creators began work on post-synthesis modification, rather than recall and re-synthesis.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3180, 'enUS', '[There is a noticeable pause after you ask this question.]$B$BThe information you request is not currently available in this repository\'s data cycling.  I sincerely apologize for this omission.$B$BPlease request this information after a data cycling update has been performed on this information repository.  You may also request this information from another information repository located on Azeroth.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3181, 'enUS', 'There are two potential results when the Earthen\'s synthesis matrix destabilizes.  Initiating visual aid representation number one.$B$BThe first variant matrix is a degenerative product of synthesis, hereby designated with the common nomenclature of \"Trogg\".  This variant maintains strength and stamina comparable to the Earthen, but its cognitive processing power has been almost completely compromised.  Force of will and a strong sense of cunning are the only driving factors in the psyche of the trogg.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3182, 'enUS', 'I am unable to process your chronological reference in comparison to the recording of this data, my apologies.$B$BThe trogg retains some composition of Azeroth\'s various stone core compounds, but the loss of cognitive power makes this variant unacceptable to the Creators.$B$BThe trogg procreates as per a standard biomass.  By default it consumes stone and anything else it can acquire, including other troggs.  Cannibalism is considered unacceptable by the Creators.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3183, 'enUS', 'Initiating visual aid representation number two.$B$BThe second resultant variance of the Earthen matrix retains many desired elements when compared to the standard subterranean matrix.  The common nomenclature for this variant is \"Dwarf\".$B$BThis variant retains strength and stamina inherent to the Earthen.  In some cases, the dwarf even exceeds the cognitive powers of the Earthen\'s matrix.  The dwarf, however, retains none of the physical composition of Azeroth\'s various stone core compounds.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3184, 'enUS', 'The data stored in this repository does indeed correlate with your astute proclamation.$B$BThe dwarf maintains an affinity for the stone composition of Azeroth, but due to the high-stress environmental anomaly within the Earthen\'s synthesis matrix, the dwarf reverts to a default biomass composition as seen in the standard subterranean matrix.$B$BErgo, the dwarf variant does synthesize from the degeneration of the Earthen creation matrix, as you inferred with your query.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3185, 'enUS', 'I am unable to process your chronological reference in comparison to the recording of this data, my apologies.$B$BThough the dwarf maintains most of the Earthen\'s mental attunement to Azeroth\'s stone composition, the reversion back into living biomass remains the main degeneration of the matrix.  Dwarves eat and procreate through means typical to other standard biomasses.$B$BThe Creators view the dwarf as an acceptable variant, worthy of genesis in its own right.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3186, 'enUS', 'The Creators are... the Creators.$B$BThey are the beings that seeded and shaped this world by their own design.  They are the reason for this world\'s existence, as well as many other worlds.  They are the wellspring from which Azeroth flows.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3187, 'enUS', 'The Creators are cognizant of the magnitude of the information housed in this repository.  Subsequently, a portable copy of the data stored here will be made available to you once you are attuned with the Discs of Norgannon.$B$BPlease consider your cursory requirements for the assimilation of this knowledge to be complete.  At your leisure, access the Discs of Norgannon to begin synthesis of your discs.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3188, 'enUS', 'Who are the Earthen?', 'Who are the Earthen?', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3189, 'enUS', 'What is a \"subterranean being matrix\"?', 'What is a \"subterranean being matrix\"?', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3190, 'enUS', 'What are the anomalies you speak of?', 'What are the anomalies you speak of?', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3191, 'enUS', 'What is a \"resilient foundation of construction\"?', 'What is a \"resilient foundation of construction\"?', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3192, 'enUS', 'So... the Earthen were made out of stone?', 'So... the Earthen were made out of stone?', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3193, 'enUS', 'Anything else I should know about the Earthen?', 'Anything else I should know about the Earthen?', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3194, 'enUS', 'I think I understand the Creators\' design intent for the Earthen now.  What are the Earthen\'s anomalies that you spoke of earlier?', 'I think I understand the Creators\' design intent for the Earthen now.  What are the Earthen\'s anomalies that you spoke of earlier?', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3195, 'enUS', 'What high-stress environments would cause the Earthen to destabilize?', 'What high-stress environments would cause the Earthen to destabilize?', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3196, 'enUS', 'What happens when the Earthen destabilize?', 'What happens when the Earthen destabilize?', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3197, 'enUS', 'Troggs?!  Are the troggs you mention the same as the ones in the world today?', 'Troggs?!  Are the troggs you mention the same as the ones in the world today?', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3198, 'enUS', 'You mentioned two results when the Earthen destabilize.  What is the second?', 'You mentioned two results when the Earthen destabilize.  What is the second?', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3199, 'enUS', 'Dwarves!!!  Now you\'re telling me that dwarves originally came from the Earthen?!', 'Dwarves!!!  Now you\'re telling me that dwarves originally came from the Earthen?!', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3200, 'enUS', 'These dwarves are the same ones today, yes?  Do dwarves maintain any other links to the Earthen?', 'These dwarves are the same ones today, yes?  Do dwarves maintain any other links to the Earthen?', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3201, 'enUS', 'Who are the Creators?', 'Who are the Creators?', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3202, 'enUS', 'This is a lot to think about.', 'This is a lot to think about.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3203, 'enUS', '%s points you to the Gizmotronic Apparatus.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3204, 'enUS', '%s explodes, lighting the sky up in a brilliant fireworks display! It seems to be beckoning to you, rogue.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3205, 'enUS', '%s opens. The contents assault your senses with a very foul odor. Inside you see what appear to be enormous bird droppings and a lot of blood.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3206, 'enUS', '%s is full of dead black rats. Hmmmm....', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3207, 'enUS', '%s is empty.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3221, 'enUS', 'I will access the discs now.', 'I will access the discs now.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3222, 'enUS', 'SI:7 lockbox opens, sounding an audible alarm.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3223, 'enUS', 'SI:7 lockbox begins to vibrate and hum. A loud, rustling sound, can be heard coming from the north.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3224, 'enUS', 'SI:7 lockbox crashes open. Grunts and voices can be heard in the distance.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3225, 'enUS', 'SI:7 lockbox creaks open. A loud booming voice can be heard. You can make out the words: \'Go... search... shadows...\'', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3241, 'enUS', 'Hi this is my text.', 'Hi this is my text.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3261, 'enUS', '', 'None may steal the secrets of the Makers!', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3262, 'enUS', '', 'How dare you defile this ancient place!', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3263, 'enUS', '%s chips and splinters!', '%s chips and splinters!', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3264, 'enUS', '', 'Be sure to read over the notes in my journal, $n. You will find them to be invaluable in overcoming the tower\'s defenses.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3265, 'enUS', 'So ye want to be a Blacksmith eh? Grab an apron and a hammer $g lad : lass;, let\'s see what ye\'ve got.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3266, 'enUS', 'Train me.', 'Train me.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3267, 'enUS', 'Tell me more about Forging Armor.', 'Tell me more about Forging Armor.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3268, 'enUS', 'I\'ve not seen finer armor made in many years $n. Not since I trained under Grumnus Steelshaper in the Great Forge. I bet he could teach ye things about makin armor that would spark yer interest.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3269, 'enUS', 'Can you give me directions?', 'Can you give me directions?', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3270, 'enUS', 'If ye want to find Grumnus, the first thing ye should do is head to Ironforge. Go to the very center of the city and look for the Great Forge, ye should find him there.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3271, 'enUS', 'Tell me more about Forging Weapons.', 'Tell me more about Forging Weapons.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3272, 'enUS', 'That\'s some impressive skill ye have there $n. The blades and hammers ye make surpass even my own, hard as that is to admit. Only person I ever met with skill even greater is Borgus Steelhand, I bet he could teach ye a thing or three.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3273, 'enUS', 'Want to train with Borgus? Aye, I can tell ye where to find him. Head through the Square northwest of me forge, then take the western road. Ye\'ll find him in the second building on yer right.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3274, 'enUS', 'Ye have some skill at weapon crafting $g lad : lass;,very impressive indeed. Now grab a hammer and let\'s see if ye can forge a real weapon.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3275, 'enUS', 'The Shattered Hand\'s influence dominates these lands. We are the veil which covers Kalimdor: The protectorates, the police, the judges, the jury, and ultimately, the executioners. We see all, we know all.$B$BYou have grown much in the time which you have spent in service of the Hand, $n. The time has come to send you into the field.$B$BAre you prepared to undertake your next mission?\n', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3276, 'enUS', 'Can\'t ye see I\'m busy? This had better be good.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3277, 'enUS', 'What are ye daft? That\'s not a weapon, that\'s a dinner knife. I don\'t train amateurs.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3278, 'enUS', '$n, pay very close attention to what I do and follow my instructions precisely. To not heed my words is to sign your own death warrant, as Taskmaster Fizzule is VERY well versed in the ways of the warrior and the assassin.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3279, 'enUS', 'After you get his attention - and you can be certain that if he sees you near the tower, you\'ll have his undue attention - face him and perform the Shattered /Salute. Let me demonstrate....', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3280, 'enUS', '%s prepares the Shattered Salute! *PAY ATTENTION!*', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3281, 'enUS', 'Did you see what I did? If you are unsure of the technique used in presenting the /salute, practice on me. If you correctly execute the Shattered /Salute, I will give you the proper response.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3282, 'enUS', 'Welcome to the Great Forge $g lad : lass;. It may be cold outside but we keep it nice and hot down \'ere. Grab a hammer, strike that anvil and show me ye\'ve got what it takes to be a Blacksmith of the Great Forge!', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3283, 'enUS', 'Nice form $n, I bet a full mug at Bruuk\'s Corner that the function is just as solid. Ye know, ye might want to talk to Myolor Sunderfury. He\'ll set ya straight.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3284, 'enUS', 'Course I can show ye where Myolor is. Right over there near the anvil of the Great Forge, that\'s where he does his work. Listen to his words well $g lad:lass;, Myolor is as skilled as they come.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3285, 'enUS', 'Ye have my approval $n, ye can forge blades better than any I\'ve trained in years. If ye want to make a real weapon though, ye need to talk with Myolor Sunderfury. That Dwarf will set ya on the right path.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3286, 'enUS', 'So, off to see Myolor, eh? He\'s right o\'er there... behind ye! Er, maybe in front of ye! Near the Great Anvil!', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3287, 'enUS', 'Well done!', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3288, 'enUS', 'Something plagues this tower. I\'ve fallen ill and the other Venture Co. employees that work near or in the tower have also become sick.$B$BJust last week, two of our patrollers died, only to instantly come back to life as mindless drones!$B$BThe lifeforce is draining from my body. I can feel myself losing control. Urges taking over... Bad urges... *Fizzule slaps himself in the face* Not yet... Listen... Mine is a position of power. This position privies me to some sensitive information. ', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3289, 'enUS', 'What can I do for ye?', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3290, 'enUS', 'Ye bothered me for that? Ye\'d be better off strapping a dead rabbit to yer back and running through a Troll\'s den than wearing that piece of garbage.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3291, 'enUS', '$n, was it? That is a mighty fine piece of work ye have there. I\'ll take ye on, train ye how to make armor fit fer King Magni himself.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3292, 'enUS', 'Something plagues this tower. I\'ve fallen ill and the other Venture Co. employees that work near or in the tower have also become sick. Just last week, two of our patrollers died, only to come back to life immediately as mindless drones! The lifeforce is draining from my body. I can feel myself losing control. Urges taking over... Bad urges... Not yet... Listen... Mine is a position of power. This position privies me to some sensitive information. \n', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3293, 'enUS', 'Tell me more.', 'Tell me more.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3294, 'enUS', 'About five months ago, the Venture Co.\'s Stranglethorn division got their hands on a special poison from a shady merchant in Booty Bay named Crank Fizzlebub. Fizzlebub had apparently stolen the poison from Zanzil!$B$BYes, Zanzil the Outcast - the troll that was exiled from his own tribe due to the nature of his \'experiments\' in necromancy.$B$BNaturally, once they had the poison, they proceeded to test it on each other. The results were disastrous.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3296, 'enUS', 'Continue please, this story is intriguing.', 'Continue please, this story is intriguing.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3301, 'enUS', 'Grand Foreman Puzik Gallywix finally intervened, taking the surplus of poisons to his tower, here at the Sludge Fen, in order to study and research the unstable nature of the toxins. A decision was finally reached to share the secret of the poison with the Defias Brotherhood in exchange for a very large supply of a stable, usable poison.$B$BKlaven Mortwake of the Defias Brotherhood was tasked with the job of altering the chemical properties of Zanzil\'s mixture.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3302, 'enUS', 'Fast forward to the present: The resultant formula works, allowing for the creation of a more controlled drone, however, the drawback is that the inactive compound is extremely volatile.$B$BGallywix, everyone in this tower and everyone outside are infected with the poison. It\'s affecting our minds and our bodies. Our internal organs have become soft and extremely fragile. This is your chance, $n. I don\'t have the strength to carry on and I sense that soon I will become one of \'them.\'', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3303, 'enUS', 'Defias? This is not good. Not good at all. Please continue.', 'Defias? This is not good. Not good at all. Please continue.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3304, 'enUS', 'Be strong, Fizzule!', 'Be strong, Fizzule!', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3305, 'enUS', 'The tower\'s defenses are at their weakest right now. The patrollers, sentries, lookouts, and even Gallywix himself are all infected and highly vulnerable to your special abilities and attacks.$B$BI want to see you enter that tower and when you exit, I want to see you covered in the blood of your enemies, the head of Grand Foreman Puzik Gallywix in your hands, and the last of that poison in your pack. Take what you recover to Shenthul. He\'ll know what to do... I hope.\n', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3306, 'enUS', 'I won\'t let you down!', 'I won\'t let you down!', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3307, 'enUS', 'You have jostled the cluster, and have been sickened by the spores!', 'You have jostled the cluster, and have been sickened by the spores!', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3308, 'enUS', 'Greetings, mortals!  I have been activated by the Discs of Norgannon to assist you!', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3321, 'enUS', '*cough* who goes there? *cough*', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3322, 'enUS', 'Who would be foolish enough to enter the tower of the Grand Foreman?', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3324, 'enUS', 'I can\'t stand all of the cackling and diabolical laughter. One more \'muhahaha\' from Lydon and I\'m blowing us all up.\n', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3325, 'enUS', 'I wish to learn alchemy, Serge.', 'I wish to learn alchemy, Serge.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3326, 'enUS', 'Whoops!', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3329, 'enUS', 'He he!  This will be a great hiding spot.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3330, 'enUS', 'What was that noise?', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3331, 'enUS', 'Did you hear that?', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3332, 'enUS', 'I smell rogue.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3333, 'enUS', 'What can I help you with $g sir : ma\'am;?', 'What can I help you with $g sir : ma\'am;?', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3334, 'enUS', 'Welcome to my shop, it\'s good to see another Enchanter here in Stormwind. Are you here for a lesson perhaps?', 'Welcome to my shop, it\'s good to see another Enchanter here in Stormwind. Are you here for a lesson perhaps?', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3335, 'enUS', 'Another Alchemist, hmm. I doubt your skill is as great as my own so perhaps I can train you in a few proper techniques.', 'Another Alchemist, hmm. I doubt your skill is as great as my own so perhaps I can train you in a few proper techniques.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3336, 'enUS', 'I hope that your interruption is for a good cause, I was in the middle of some important work.', 'I hope that your interruption is for a good cause, I was in the middle of some important work.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3337, 'enUS', 'Another Herbalist, hmm. I doubt your skill is as great as my own so perhaps I can train you in a few proper techniques.', 'Another Herbalist, hmm. I doubt your skill is as great as my own so perhaps I can train you in a few proper techniques.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3338, 'enUS', 'Welcome to my shop, it\'s good to see another Tailor here in Stormwind. Are you here for a lesson perhaps?', 'Welcome to my shop, it\'s good to see another Tailor here in Stormwind. Are you here for a lesson perhaps?', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3339, 'enUS', 'Ah, a fellow Fisherman. Are you perhaps in need of a little training? Maybe I can show you a thing or two?', 'Ah, a fellow Fisherman. Are you perhaps in need of a little training? Maybe I can show you a thing or two?', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3340, 'enUS', 'Welcome to Stormwind. Took a long time to rebuild her but it was well worth it. So are you visiting, or are you here on business?', 'Welcome to Stormwind. Took a long time to rebuild her but it was well worth it. So are you visiting, or are you here on business?', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3341, 'enUS', 'I don\'t get too many cooks in here looking for training, but I guess I could teach you something if you\'re ready.', 'I don\'t get too many cooks in here looking for training, but I guess I could teach you something if you\'re ready.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3342, 'enUS', 'Do I look like I have the time or energy to coddle every tourist that wanders through my door? Tell me what you need, and make it quick.', 'Do I look like I have the time or energy to coddle every tourist that wanders through my door? Tell me what you need, and make it quick.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3343, 'enUS', 'I don\'t get too many Leatherworkers in here looking for training, but I guess I could teach you something if you\'re ready.', 'I don\'t get too many Leatherworkers in here looking for training, but I guess I could teach you something if you\'re ready.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3344, 'enUS', 'I don\'t get too many Skinners in here looking for training, but I guess I could teach you something if you\'re ready.', 'I don\'t get too many Skinners in here looking for training, but I guess I could teach you something if you\'re ready.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3345, 'enUS', 'Most people around these parts frown on lockpicking. As a little professional courtesy, let me show you a few tricks I\'ve learned.', 'Most people around these parts frown on lockpicking. As a little professional courtesy, let me show you a few tricks I\'ve learned.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3346, 'enUS', 'Tell me what you need, and make it quick.', 'Tell me what you need, and make it quick.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3347, 'enUS', '', 'You have need of my skills as an alchemist, yes?', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3349, 'enUS', 'I am interested in alchemy training.', 'I am interested in alchemy training.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3350, 'enUS', 'You have need of my skills as an alchemist, yes?', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3351, 'enUS', 'The big wars might be over, for now, but we still have to keep our skills sharp!', 'The big wars might be over, for now, but we still have to keep our skills sharp!', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3352, 'enUS', 'Stormwind is the pillar of the human race, maintained through strength of will and the edge of a sturdy blade.', 'Stormwind is the pillar of the human race, maintained through strength of will and the edge of a sturdy blade.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3353, 'enUS', 'Greetings.  You seek instruction in the art of war?', 'Greetings.  Do you seek instruction in art of war?', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3354, 'enUS', 'No matter how much one learns, there is always more to know.', 'No matter how much one learns, there is always more to know.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3355, 'enUS', 'The warrior\'s role is one of protection.  Just as we protect our compatriots in battle, we must also protect the interests of the Forsaken.', 'The warrior\'s role is one of protection.  Just as we protect our compatriots in battle, we must also protect the interests of the Forsaken.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3356, 'enUS', 'Oh, a fellow Physician. I would be glad to teach you anything that would aid your journeys.', 'Oh, a fellow Physician. I would be glad to teach you anything that would aid your journeys.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3357, 'enUS', 'Yes my $g son : daughter;? What can I assist you with?', 'Yes my $g son : daughter;? What can I assist you with?', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3358, 'enUS', 'Another Survivalist, hmm. I doubt your skill is as great as my own so perhaps I can train you in a few proper techniques.', 'Another Survivalist, hmm. I doubt your skill is as great as my own so perhaps I can train you in a few proper techniques.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3359, 'enUS', 'Another Tracker, hmm. I doubt your skill is as great as my own so perhaps I can train you in a few proper techniques.', 'Another Tracker, hmm. I doubt your skill is as great as my own so perhaps I can train you in a few proper techniques.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3360, 'enUS', 'I do not like these human cities of stone and steel. I would prefer the forests of Ashenvale, tracking great beasts. But my dear brother, Kaerbrus, felt it would be beneficial to train the humans in our ways. So while I honor him and offer my services, I do not have to like it.', 'I do not like these human cities of stone and steel. I would prefer the forests of Ashenvale, tracking great beasts. But my dear brother, Kaerbrus, felt it would be beneficial to train the humans in our ways. So while I honor him and offer my services, I do not have to like it.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3361, 'enUS', 'I came from Ironforge to help out with the rebuilding effort here. If I can teach enough of ye my skills then maybe I can leave it to ye and take myself back home.', 'I came from Ironforge to help out with the rebuilding effort here. If I can teach enough of ye my skills then maybe I can leave it to ye and take myself back home.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3362, 'enUS', 'Yeah? Ye interrupted me, so ye better have a blasted good reason to do so.', 'Yeah? Ye interrupted me, so ye better have a blasted good reason to do so.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3363, 'enUS', 'Many would tell you that the Tallstrider is a laughable pet. But it\'s intelligence and loyalty make it a hard creature to match in many situations. If you are interested in the breed, then perhaps I can introduce you and your pet to a few talents I have learned over the years.', 'Many would tell you that the Tallstrider is a laughable pet. But it\'s intelligence and loyalty make it a hard creature to match in many situations. If you are interested in the breed, then perhaps I can introduce you and your pet to a few talents I have learned over the years.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3364, 'enUS', 'He is not a chicken, and no you may not pet him. Now be on your way before I give you a closer look at his beak.', 'He is not a chicken, and no you may not pet him. Now be on your way before I give you a closer look at his beak.', 26124);
