INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3473, 'enUS', 'It\'s fascinating... I have heard orcs proclaim the odor of humans to be sickening and I have heard humans proclaim the odor of orcs to be wretched; yet, to me, all of the races of these lands give off the same odor: The foul, dizzying scent of greed.$B$BDo you doubt the validity of my claim? Do you not see these things that run your life as merely runoff from the greed which dictates your every decision?$B$BSo be it. As it was greed that displaced me from my home, it shall be greed that takes me back.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3474, 'enUS', 'So you have returned to help Kum\'isha, $r? Do not worry, the pang that you feel in the pit of your stomach is merely your willpower collapsing.$B$BThankfully, you will not need willpower for this collection. I am certain that you will enjoy the trinkets I will have waiting for you upon your return with the item.\n', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3475, 'enUS', 'Success, the rift is open!! My brethren, rise and return home! The Outland awaits!', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3476, 'enUS', 'Hurry brothers! You must go now! I do not know how much longer the rift will remain open!', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3477, 'enUS', 'And now you know why I live in a crater.', '', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3478, 'enUS', 'War is a bloody, messy ordeal full of pain, suffering and death. But those that survive come back with a new respect for life. Not to mention a collection of stories to tell around the bar, full of bravery and courage. So tell me $g lad : lass;, are you here to make some stories? or just to hear some of mine?', 'War is a bloody, messy ordeal full of pain, suffering and death. But those that survive come back with a new respect for life. Not to mention a collection of stories to tell around the bar, full of bravery and courage. So tell me $g lad : lass;, are you here to make some stories? or just to hear some of mine?', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3479, 'enUS', 'I wish to fight!', 'I wish to fight!', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3481, 'enUS', 'Then head over to Bena\'s Alchemy on the middle rise and talk to Bena herself.  She will be able to help you master the art of potion brewing.', 'Then head over to Bena\'s Alchemy on the middle rise and talk to Bena herself.  She will be able to help you master the art of potion brewing.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3482, 'enUS', 'Looking to learn how to work an anvil and hammer, eh?  Karn Stonehoof can teach you how.  He has a smithy set up on the lower rise by the pond.', 'Looking to learn how to work an anvil and hammer, eh?  Karn Stonehoof can teach you how.  He has a smithy set up on the lower rise by the pond.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3483, 'enUS', 'There is no finer cook in Thunder Bluff than Aska Mistrunner.  Mmmmm, I can smell what she is cooking from here.  Head over to her kitchen located on the high rise.\n\nDrat... now I am hungry.', 'There is no finer cook in Thunder Bluff than Aska Mistrunner.  Mmmmm, I can smell what she is cooking from here.  Head over to her kitchen located on the high rise.\n\nDrat... now I am hungry.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3484, 'enUS', 'Check out Dawnstrider Enchanters on the middle rise then.  Teg will be more than happy to help you in whatever way he can.', 'Check out Dawnstrider Enchanters on the middle rise then.  Teg will be more than happy to help you in whatever way he can.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3485, 'enUS', 'First Aid is always a nice skill to have.  Many a time during battle has it saved my hide.  Visit Spiritual Healing on the Spirit Rise.  Pand Stonebinder can teach you all you need to know to save your hide as well.', 'First Aid is always a nice skill to have.  Many a time during battle has it saved my hide.  Visit Spiritual Healing on the Spirit Rise.  Pand Stonebinder can teach you all you need to know to save your hide as well.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3486, 'enUS', 'Don\'t blame you for taking up fishing.  Mulgore has some the best fishing spots in Southern Kalimdor and Mountaintop Bait & Tackle on the high rise has all of the gear you\'ll need to take advantage of it.\n\nTell Kah Mistrunner that I sent ya!', 'Don\'t blame you for taking up fishing.  Mulgore has some the best fishing spots in Southern Kalimdor and Mountaintop Bait & Tackle on the high rise has all of the gear you\'ll need to take advantage of it.\n\nTell Kah Mistrunner that I sent ya!', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3487, 'enUS', 'Komin Winterhoof at Holistic Herbalism is the one you want to talk to then.  He can be found on the middle rise.', 'Komin Winterhoof at Holistic Herbalism is the one you want to talk to then.  He can be found on the middle rise.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3488, 'enUS', 'Go see Una at Thunder Bluff Armorers then.  It can be found on the middle rise.', 'Go see Una at Thunder Bluff Armorers then.  It can be found on the middle rise.', 26124);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text_locale` VALUES (3489, 'enUS', 'Brek Stonehoof can be found at Stonehoof Geology on the lower rise and can teach you the proper way to harvest precious ores and gems.', 'Brek Stonehoof can be found at Stonehoof Geology on the lower rise and can teach you the proper way to harvest precious ores and gems.', 26124);
